{"tid":905693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】恐怖！弟弟坐購物車裡　他推下扶梯害破頭","createTime":"2018-11-17T10:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T13:04:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd38aa6c5af042477881f949d7d02bbea9c19194","tid":905693,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一對小兄弟日前與媽媽同赴購物中心，但哥哥卻在沒有人注意時，將坐在手推車裡的弟弟推下手扶梯，推車立刻失去平衡翻覆，將弟弟摔出摔至手扶梯並壓過去，導致臉上布滿鮮血、嚎啕大哭，而這時哥哥則僵住不知該如何是好，所幸旁人見狀趕緊上前扶起並送醫。<br />\n《每日郵報》報導，俄羅斯尼亞甘一處購物中心「Oasis Plaza」日前來了一對小兄弟，其中穿著黑色背心的哥哥，推著坐在購物車裡的弟弟到手扶梯前，沒想到哥哥將購物車用力推到向下移動的手扶梯後，雙手就這樣放開，推車也立刻翻覆摔出弟弟，重摔至手扶梯上，旁人見狀直奔上前扶起，隨後保全也迅速奔下手扶梯了解狀況。<br />\n目擊者卡馬佛瓦（Albina Khamavova）表示，男童摔出購物車後撞破額頭，臉部及衣物都被染上紅色鮮血，男童在等待救護車時，起初是站著嚎啕大哭，但卻在救護人員到達前暈倒。這對小兄弟的母親約在事發後5分鐘跑到現場，並開始教訓推著購物車的哥哥。<br />\n受傷的弟弟在父母的陪同之下到醫院就醫，不過名字沒有被公布出來。事後警方調查，認為兩個男童的母親的責任最大，因為當時她沒有仔細看管兩名孩小，才導致悲劇發生，更可能須被罰款。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181117/640_ceeaa09e1448fe879e881ec27caacb42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181117%2F640_ceeaa09e1448fe879e881ec27caacb42.jpg&h=9721a9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n片係link入面<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181117/1468299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181117%2F1468299%2F&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=af2bd69e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181117%2F1468299%2F&h=ad2f5c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181117/1468299/</a>"},{"pid":"e322d54519e8cd63f37004913ea01620d4932c95","tid":905693,"uid":86673,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"仲以為係大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954cdb03bd1ab77c31cdd723e91d29b9ca3fbe1a","tid":905693,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:52:23.000Z","msg":"唸住趁細個殺人無罪拿拿臨整死細佬,第時分身家分多份"},{"pid":"d75f3e5f8cf4b2fcf540667f93c81ade29cc1185","tid":905693,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b31d813c0072207a6c95f04d8cf7d9024ab58c7","tid":905693,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e322d54519e8cd63f37004913ea01620d4932c95","tid":905693,"uid":86673,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"仲以為係大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1053a28cf6281c0d3d63a304fc4c6ea2cdabfbf6","tid":905693,"uid":85557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"之後行得走得無咩事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215496650a7c682fd2822af2f4aabfcc1ef93508","tid":905693,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"954cdb03bd1ab77c31cdd723e91d29b9ca3fbe1a","tid":905693,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:52:23.000Z","msg":"唸住趁細個殺人無罪拿拿臨整死細佬,第時分身家分多份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"我諗呀哥係想睇架車sir落去，點知無諗過電梯唔係平面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980f0b00565f5a962a2aa2302d1f8f79e63cb60f","tid":905693,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1053a28cf6281c0d3d63a304fc4c6ea2cdabfbf6","tid":905693,"uid":85557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11: